{"tid":2344863,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"三國志14 之 曹老闆最撚勁","createTime":"2020-12-29T05:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T07:59:31.000Z","uid":198730,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e135bc0dcac7e50c4c89c87cd073a613528c6114","tid":2344863,"uid":198730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:41:49.000Z","msg":"其實有啲行軍三十幾四十年嘅魏將真係好用<br />\n1.曹仁<br />\n2.曹真 （唔算老嘅其實又）<br />\n3.張郃<br />\n雖然唔係啲咩趙雲級數，但用落真係「有feel」。<br />\n我唔知點形容好，我覺得老將就係寶，有時幾羨慕啲長命嘅人，可以經歷到咁多歷史時刻，而自己又可以名留千古咁先爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c4a4686de39aef85a2dc0f62d04f1ff6a76200","tid":2344863,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"多人才 如果官渡之戰之前玩 真係可以拎晒袁紹啲武將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3e58a1ea86882704f7f605e3eb487b3285b3a7","tid":2344863,"uid":34970,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"玩三國志只要攞到曹魏嘅班底已經破左局"},{"pid":"af1a23a6aceadfa48cf54e91c76cad393bca39cf","tid":2344863,"uid":198730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"207年劉備開局，超級難度，點打好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189e99623ac24491bc4aa281a316c709404c5884","tid":2344863,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"諸葛村夫用兵最奇"},{"pid":"1af4d231db583306b6c1e78065948a80fa1d3834","tid":2344863,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af1a23a6aceadfa48cf54e91c76cad393bca39cf","tid":2344863,"uid":198730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"207年劉備開局，超級難度，點打好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"入蜀=爆機"}]}